case.title: Quirky, funny ,curvy? Needing a fit strong man - 37 (london)
case.text:
I need to be worked out :-) ! anyone in the NW area like to get me fit ?
this is a cheeky ad, but am a normal girl, wanting to find a normal man but in the mean time , I wouldn't mind to find someone who likes to walk, run swim and work me out
Please take it a bit with humour
only attracted to confident ,strong and fun
